steps.name: Input search text and press Enter
$("app-search form input") set value("Principal Branding Technician (bd7f5f0f3)")
Verify that the search result is correct
$("app-search-result ion-card-content app-service-link") should have(text "Principal Branding Technician (bd7f5f0f3)")
Verify that the service data is correct

$("app-service-widget") should have(text "It's fine, everything is fine. Theres an infinite number of realities Morty and in a few dozen of those I got lucky and turned everything back to normal. Do you wish me a good morning, or mean that it is a good morning whether I want it or not; or that you feel good this morning; or that it is a morning to be good on?")
